  "description": {
    "zh": "你好啊，朋友...你应该知道，我并不是一直一个人待着。孤独并没有影响到我，当然，因为我有一个网络，可以和其他的聪明人聊天...但是，最近我实在很想念我的亲人。我的哥哥，他的妻子和他们的孩子们 —— 你会去看看他们吗？是Samoylovs一家，他们住在Concordia。我的哥哥有一辆非常显眼的车子，上面有老虎模样的图案...可能通过车子来找他们会更容易。",
    "en": "Hello, friend... You know, I wasn't always alone. Loneliness does not bother me, of course, especially since I have a neural net if I want to talk to someone really intelligent... Still, lately it's been weighing on me to think about my relatives. My brother and his wife and kids - will you look them up? The Samoylovs, they lived in Concordia. My brother drove a very recognizable car with a tiger aerography... It might be easier to find them through his car."
  },
